jobs.prompt:
Write concrete v2 manifest JSON for 5 app templates using ONLY these existing modules:

metric, stat-row, chart, activity-feed, status-grid, markdown, key-value, text-input, intent-box, dropdown-select, button-row, file-drop, dispatch-form, search-panel, document-processor, data-pipeline, workflow-status, bug-card, model-card, registry-browser

Modules go in a 4x4 grid (A1-D4). Spans: 1x1, 2x1, 1x2, 2x2.

Module config examples:
- metric: {endpoint, path, label, format, color}
- chart: {endpoint, path, type, xKey, yKey}
- activity-feed: {endpoint, title}
- status-grid: {endpoint, title, columns}
- key-value: {items: [{label, value}]}
- button-row: {actions: [{label, variant}]}
- data-pipeline: {steps: [{name}]}
- markdown: {content}
- text-input: {placeholder, worldPath}
- dropdown-select: {options, label, worldPath}

Build these 5:
1. CRM Dashboard (id: crm-dashboard)
2. Project Tracker (id: project-tracker)
3. Analytics Dashboard (id: analytics-dashboard)
4. Content Calendar (id: content-calendar)
5. Team Status Board (id: team-status)

Each manifest format:
{"version": 2, "grid": "4x4", "quadrants": {"A1": {"module": "...", "span": "...", "config": {...}}, ...}}

Make them look like real apps. Use realistic placeholder data in configs where needed.
